11:54.796 --> 11:56.289
OK, Cinderella, what gives?

11:56.332 --> 11:57.662
Your tiara on too tight?

11:57.705 --> 12:00.463
I'm just congratulating a
friend on all his hard work.

12:00.505 --> 12:01.965
Speaking of, why don't you come over

12:02.007 --> 12:03.767
afterwards to my place and crash?

12:03.809 --> 12:06.136
We'll talk about who
hooked up with whom,

12:06.178 --> 12:07.704
binge out on ice cream.

12:07.746 --> 12:09.539
Our first slumber party.

12:09.581 --> 12:11.541
- What do you think?
- Okay, I'm scared.

12:11.583 --> 12:14.511
<i>(SPOOKY MUSIC)</i>

12:14.553 --> 12:15.545
<i>♪</i>

12:15.587 --> 12:17.180
(SCREAMING)

12:17.222 --> 12:21.418
<i>♪</i>

12:21.460 --> 12:24.621
(CHAINSAW WHIRRING)

12:24.663 --> 12:26.723
Oh, I'm sorry, I couldn't resist.

12:26.765 --> 12:28.391
Felix, not funny!

12:28.433 --> 12:29.793
What are you doing here?

12:29.835 --> 12:31.261
Amy said the haunted house was epic,

12:31.303 --> 12:32.696
so I decided to volunteer.

12:33.237 --> 12:34.963
Also, she said she can't be scared.

12:35.005 --> 12:36.665
I'm about to prove her wrong.

12:36.707 --> 12:38.809
You know the part at the end,
right when you think it's over?

12:38.852 --> 12:40.068
That's when I come out.

12:40.110 --> 12:43.672
(CHAINSAW WHIRRING)

12:43.714 --> 12:45.321
- (YELLS)
- Felix!

12:46.550 --> 12:47.476
No...

12:47.518 --> 12:50.178
- That was so fun.
- (LAUGHS)

12:50.220 --> 12:51.513
What do we do now?

12:51.555 --> 12:54.282
Now's the part when you kiss.

12:54.324 --> 12:55.984
