- Nobody asked you.

12:56.026 --> 12:58.987
<i>(REDINHO'S "PLAYING WITH FIRE")</i>

12:59.029 --> 13:00.856
<i>♪</i>

13:00.898 --> 13:02.013
He's right, though.

13:02.056 --> 13:04.033
This is where the kissing
usually happens.

13:04.075 --> 13:05.735
<i>♪</i>

13:05.777 --> 13:07.470
<i>♪ Girl you got me ♪</i>

13:07.512 --> 13:09.372
<i>♪ Playing with fire ♪</i>

13:09.414 --> 13:12.242
<i>♪</i>

13:12.284 --> 13:14.677
<i>♪ I can't resist this desire ♪</i>

13:14.719 --> 13:16.346
(CHAINSAW WHIRRING)

13:16.388 --> 13:18.415
<i>♪</i>

13:18.457 --> 13:19.949
Felix?

13:19.991 --> 13:22.352
<i>♪ Girl you got me playing with fire ♪</i>

13:22.394 --> 13:25.255
I'm guessing you two know each other.

13:25.297 --> 13:28.031
<i>♪ I can't resist this desire ♪</i>

13:32.979 --> 13:35.531
<i>♪</i>

13:37.116 --> 13:39.444
Felix. Are you okay?

13:39.487 --> 13:43.482
Uh, actually, I'm a bit
angry and a little bit sad.

13:43.524 --> 13:48.020
Working on identifying my
feelings as they come out.

13:48.062 --> 13:49.955
My sponsor said I
should write them down.

13:49.997 --> 13:51.757
Felix, that kiss meant nothing.

13:51.799 --> 13:54.293
Amy just came here tonight to
make out with random strangers.

13:54.335 --> 13:56.762
Really? 'Cause, uh...

13:56.804 --> 13:58.530
she told me she was just coming

13:58.572 --> 14:00.599
to be your wing woman.

14:00.641 --> 14:02.034
Oh.

14:02.076 --> 14:06.338
Look, Amy can kiss whoever
the heck she wants,

14:06.380 --> 14:09.475
and it's not like I expect
her to wait for me.

14:09.517 --> 14:11.510
It's just I'm still jealous,

14:11.552 --> 14:13.412
even though I know I shouldn't be.

14:13.454 --> 14:15.981
Look, Amy knows about your recovery.

14:16.023 --> 14:18.817
And... and she doesn't drink.

14:18.859 --> 14:20.486
Why can't you two date?

14:20.528 --> 14:22.254
Because I need to get
my own house in order

14:22.296 --> 14:24.156
before I let anyone else in.

14:24.198 --> 14:27.226
Otherwise, I'll just
keep on screwing it up.

14:27.268 --> 14:29.742
<i>(SOFT PIANO MUSIC)</i>

14:30.471 --> 14:31.980
That makes sense.

14:34.141 --> 14:37.769
♪ Baby ♪

14:37.811 --> 14:39.872
There you are.

14:39.914 --> 14:41.340
Hey, sailor.

14:41.382 --> 14:43.041
It's been a while since
you've been in my port.

14:43.083 --> 14:44.376
Hey, Brandi.

14:44.418 --> 14:46.678
Uh, sorry, I thought
you were someone else.

14:46.720 --> 14:48.146
It's Halloween.

14:48.188 --> 14:50.215
I can be whoever you want me to be.

14:50.257 --> 14:52.017
♪

14:52.059 --> 14:55.153
♪ I will always be ♪

14:55.195 --> 14:56.622
Sorry. Excuse me.

14:56.664 --> 14:57.856
Wait, Karma.

14:57.898 --> 14:59.324
Wait, that was not what it looked like.

14:59.366 --> 15:01.126
I was actually looking to talk to you

15:01.168 --> 15:03.395
and, I don't know, I
got my witch switched.

15:03.437 --> 15:04.730
Liam, about what I said earlier...

15:04.772 --> 15:06.498
Yeah, I wanted to talk
to you about that, too.

15:06.540 --> 15:10.502
Look, I hate to say this,
but just because I want us

15:10.544 --> 15:12.638
to get back together
doesn't mean we should.

15:12.680 --> 15:14.006
Wait, it doesn't?

15:14.048 --> 15:16.208
I'm kind of confused.

15:16.250 --> 15:17.809
I'm not ready.

15:17.851 --> 15:20.178
I think the universe has
been trying to tell me that,

15:20.220 --> 15:22.014
but I've been refusing to listen.

15:22.056 --> 15:23.148
Look, Karma, I told you, that...

15:23.190 --> 15:25.918
Just let me finish.

15:25.960 --> 15:28.120
Liam, you're my first love.

15:28.162 --> 15:31.356
And I spend an embarrassing
amount of time

15:31.398 --> 15:33.058
daydreaming about our future together.

15:33.100 --> 15:37.229
But if we start it now,

15:37.271 --> 15:38.964
I'm pretty sure I'll just screw it up

15:39.006 --> 15:40.732
by being jealous or insecure.

15:40.774 --> 15:42.234
I think it's been
pretty well established

15:42.276 --> 15:45.203
that I am also capable
of screwing things up.

15:45.245 --> 15:46.772
I did not mean that literally.

15:46.814 --> 15:48.407
(LAUGHS)

15:48.449 --> 15:51.109
So maybe we just try being friends?

15:51.151 --> 15:53.744
Friends. Yeah.

15:54.069 --> 15:56.196
Yeah, let's, uh, let's give that a shot.

15:56.238 --> 15:57.230
Okay.

15:57.272 --> 16:00.434
Then as your friend, I wish you luck

16:00.476 --> 16:02.202
in your witch hunting.

16:02.244 --> 16:04.171
I'm just kidding.

16:04.213 --> 16:06.306
(WHISPERING) I hope you strike out.

16:06.348 --> 16:10.243
♪

16:10.285 --> 16:11.545
Well, she's smiling.

16:11.587 --> 16:12.813
That's a good sign.

16:12.855 --> 16:15.749
Yeah, we're gonna try and be friends.

16:15.791 --> 16:17.017
And I'm okay with that.

16:17.059 --> 16:18.618
(GAGGING)

16:18.660 --> 16:20.020
Are you choking?

16:20.062 --> 16:21.988
(GAGGING)

16:22.030 --> 16:23.723
(GRUNTING)

16:23.765 --> 16:26.693
<i>(INTENSE MUSIC)</i>

16:26.735 --> 16:29.796
<i>♪</i>

16:29.838 --> 16:31.731
No, no, no!

16:31.773 --> 16:33.733
Stop (BLEEP) my mom!

16:33.775 --> 16:35.602
(SPITS)

16:35.644 --> 16:36.603
(COUGHS)

16:36.645 --> 16:39.973
- Whoa.
- Is she okay?

16:40.015 --> 16:41.541
Oh. Thank you.

16:41.583 --> 16:42.809
Yeah.

16:42.851 --> 16:46.012
<i>(LIVELY MUSIC)</i>

16:46.054 --> 16:47.080
- Rawr!
- (SCREAMING)

16:47.122 --> 16:50.283
(CHAINSAW WHIRRING)

16:50.325 --> 16:52.486
♪

16:52.528 --> 16:54.254
Can we talk?

16:54.296 --> 16:56.189
Sure.

16:56.231 --> 16:58.024
Look, about the kiss,
I didn't know that...

16:58.066 --> 16:59.526
Look, Amy, you don't
have to feel guilty.

16:59.568 --> 17:01.428
Yeah, I do. We have a thing, don't we?

17:01.470 --> 17:03.105
Well, no, we can't have a thing.

17:03.148 --> 17:04.030
Not now.

17:04.071 --> 17:06.199
Well, yeah, not until New Year's Eve.

17:06.241 --> 17:09.536
My lips were just killing time.

17:09.578 --> 17:13.573
Look, Amy, it's not fair of me
to ask you to wait until then.

17:13.615 --> 17:14.875
What if I want to?

17:14.916 --> 17:16.910
It's too much pressure.

17:16.952 --> 17:20.446
If something's gonna happen
between us, it'll happen.

17:20.489 --> 17:21.915
If it's meant to be.

17:21.957 --> 17:24.851
But until then...

17:24.893 --> 17:26.329
I release you.

17:27.194 --> 17:29.823
Or something that
doesn't sound so weird.

17:29.865 --> 17:31.424
(BOTH LAUGH)

17:31.466 --> 17:33.560
♪

17:33.602 --> 17:35.562
Okay.

17:35.604 --> 17:36.796
If you're sure.

17:36.838 --> 17:38.698
I am.

17:38.740 --> 17:40.867
Now if you'll excuse me,

17:40.909 --> 17:42.669
I've got more horny kids to scare.

17:42.711 --> 17:44.210
(CHAINSAW WHIRRING)

17:45.684 --> 17:46.911
<i>Seriously, Shane?</i>

17:46.953 --> 17:48.724
You think I want to do
your mom doggie-style

17:48.767 --> 17:49.993
in the middle of a school party?

17:50.035 --> 17:51.161
Are you saying you would do her

17:51.203 --> 17:52.929
under different circumstances?

17:52.971 --> 17:54.735
No, I would never have
sex with your mother!

17:54.778 --> 17:56.533
Well, you did have sex with my sister!

17:56.575 --> 17:57.867
(SCOFFS)

17:57.909 --> 18:01.104
(TECHNO MUSIC PLAYING)

18:01.146 --> 18:02.105
Shane...

18:02.147 --> 18:03.573
I know, I thought I was over it,

18:03.615 --> 18:07.611
but I guess my subconscious
doesn't agree.

18:07.653 --> 18:09.045
- I'm sorry...
- Stop.

18:09.087 --> 18:11.314
Okay, you don't need to apologize.

18:11.356 --> 18:13.817
I did sleep with Sasha.

18:13.859 --> 18:15.685
I wish I could undo it, but I can't.

18:15.727 --> 18:17.020
Can't undo my sister.

18:17.062 --> 18:19.155
No, but I can make it right.

18:19.197 --> 18:21.662
I can earn your trust
back, and to do that,

18:22.834 --> 18:24.127
I think I should move out.

18:24.169 --> 18:27.330
What? Liam, what are you talking about?

18:27.372 --> 18:28.565
You have nowhere to go.

18:28.607 --> 18:29.733
Don't worry about it, man.

18:29.775 --> 18:31.334
I'll... I'll figure something out.

18:31.376 --> 18:33.670
The important thing is that
you know there is zero risk

18:33.712 --> 18:35.639
of me ever sleeping with
your family members.

18:35.681 --> 18:43.820
♪

18:44.722 --> 18:46.216
Just so you know,

18:46.258 --> 18:48.685
I'm fine if you sleep with my cousins.

18:48.727 --> 18:51.421
(LAUGHS)

18:51.463 --> 18:53.490
Hey, boyfriend.

18:53.532 --> 18:54.791
What's that?

18:54.833 --> 18:57.027
You just got back from the gym?

18:57.069 --> 18:58.728
You benched 300 pounds?

18:58.770 --> 19:00.730
Wow, good for you, baby.

19:00.772 --> 19:02.098
<i>(TENSE MUSIC)</i>

19:02.140 --> 19:03.433
(YELPS)

19:03.475 --> 19:05.502
(THUNDER CRASHES)

19:05.544 --> 19:06.503
(GASPS)

19:06.545 --> 19:07.470
