19:07.512 --> 19:08.705
(BLEEP) it!

19:08.747 --> 19:14.277
<i>♪</i>

19:14.319 --> 19:15.745
(THUNDER CRASHES)

19:15.787 --> 19:16.980
<i>♪</i>

19:17.022 --> 19:18.348
