19:18.390 --> 19:21.324
(GROANING)

19:22.393 --> 19:23.687
(THUNDER CRASHES)

19:23.729 --> 19:25.789
Don't even think about suing me.

19:25.831 --> 19:28.358
You made aggressive moves
towards me back there.

19:28.400 --> 19:30.727
I parked next to you.

19:30.769 --> 19:34.731
Just be glad I don't really
have a gun in my purse.

19:34.773 --> 19:36.132
You shouldn't drive home.

19:36.174 --> 19:38.334
I'll let you crash on my couch.

19:38.376 --> 19:41.538
My car now is my home, so
it's not much of a drive.

19:41.580 --> 19:42.540
Don't care.

19:43.648 --> 19:44.741
Nice apartment.

19:44.783 --> 19:45.975
It's a condo!

19:46.017 --> 19:47.777
<i>(LIVELY MUSIC)</i>

19:47.819 --> 19:50.380
Okay, so maybe I was waiting for Felix.

19:50.422 --> 19:52.348
But not anymore.

19:52.390 --> 19:54.017
He released me.

19:54.059 --> 19:56.152
Eh, it's only two months away.

19:56.194 --> 19:57.620
A lot can happen in two months.

19:57.662 --> 19:59.355
What about you and Liam?

19:59.397 --> 20:00.757
I realized you were right.

20:00.799 --> 20:02.459
I need to be single for a bit.

20:02.501 --> 20:03.727
Get comfortable being alone.

20:03.769 --> 20:05.695
Well, luckily, you're not alone.

20:05.737 --> 20:07.197
You've got me.

20:07.239 --> 20:08.965
You always know what to say.

20:09.007 --> 20:10.400
What do you say we ditch this party

20:10.442 --> 20:12.635
and go eat our weight in
leftover Halloween candy?

20:12.677 --> 20:14.871
Sounds like heaven.

20:14.913 --> 20:16.239
<i>(SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC)</i>

20:16.281 --> 20:18.007
Amy?

20:18.049 --> 20:19.075
I thought that was you!

20:19.117 --> 20:22.345
Oh, my God. Sabrina!

20:22.387 --> 20:23.947
Look, Karma, it's Sabrina!

20:23.989 --> 20:27.113
